summary: After graduating from university, I worked in different companies abroad as a Physics Teacher for 10 years. I taught high school classes and taught and mentored students for the International Olympics. I wanted to change my field of work from education to IT and I improved myself in this regard. I started a bootcamp(Fenyx Academy) in Amsterdam. I have just graduated from Fenyx Academy. I have learned Python, Data Engineering, Data Analyze, Data Visualization, and how to use Machine Learning models. Now I'm looking for a job as a junior position ☺️
